= [[<<SetTitle "SahrisWiki" display=True>>]] =

Welcome to [[SahrisWiki]]'s development wiki and development environment. 

This is [[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki_software|Wiki Software]], a [[http://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki|Wiki]] Engine.

For more information see [[Docs]].

Try this wiki out for yourself!
* Navigate to [[SandBox]]
* Hover over **Functions** (//bottom left of the page//)
* Click **Edit**
* Enter some text and click **Save**

**NB**: To help circumvent SPAM Authentication and Authorization has been turned on. [[+login|Login]] with {{{admin:admin}}} before editing these pages.

Want to install the latest development version? Perform these steps:

# Ensure you have: [[http://www.python.org/|Python]], [[http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools|setuptools]] or [[http://pypi.python.org/pypi/distribute|distribute]] and [[http://mercurial.selenic.com/|Mercurial]] installed on your system.

# Clone and Install circuits-dev
<<code lang="sh">>
$ hg clone https://bitbucket.org/prologic/circuits-dev/
$ cd circuits-dev
$ python setup.py develop
<</code>>

# Clone and Install sahriswiki
<<code lang="sh">>
$ hg clone https://bitbucket.org/prologic/sahriswiki/
$ cd sahriswiki
$ python setup.py develop
<</code>>

# Run {{{sahriswiki}}}
<<code lang="sh">>
$ sahriswiki --help
<</code>>

Enjoy! :)
